ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v24.group

Class ORD_O04_RESPONSE

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v24.group.ORD_O04_RESPONSE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class ORD_O04_RESPONSE
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a ORD_O04_RESPONSE group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: ORD_O04_PATIENT (a Group object) optional
    • 2: ORD_O04_ORDER_DIET (a Group object) repeating
    • 3: ORD_O04_ORDER_TRAY (a Group object) optional repeating
